text: National Highway 766EE, commonly referred to as NH 766EE is a national highway in India. It is a secondary route of National Highway 66. NH-766EE runs in the state of Karnataka in India. == Route == NH766EE connects Hattikeri and Belekeri Port in the state of Karnataka. == Junctions == : Terminal near Hattikeri. == See also == * List of National Highways in India * List of National Highways in India by state == References == == External links == * NH 766EE on OpenStreetMap Category:National highways in India Category:National Highways in Karnataka
